| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1351 — Recovery Inhibition (BrainCipher)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 68ed396c-df34-57d0-903e-e3167a471bd0"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
